-- Yemen to Establish Security Unit at Country's Airports, Altomar.net Says
-- B y   M o h a m m e d   H a t e m
-- 2010-11-12T17:44:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-12/yemen-to-establish-security-unit-at-country-s-airports-altomar-net-says.html
Yemeni Interior Minister Mutahar
Rashad al-Masri has decided to establish a security unit at
airports in the country, Almotamar.net, the website of the
ruling party, reported, citing unnamed government sources.  The unit will work on developing and upgrading security
services and train airport workers to boost the protection
measures of airports and aircraft against any sabotage and
terrorist acts, the website said.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Mohammed Hatem Hasan Ali in Dubai at 
